<br>
I hate it when people take electronic communication (email, message boards, etc.) and consider it not worth the time and effort to use some halfway readable verbage.<br>
<br>
It's a pet peeve of mine.<br>
<br>
Read just the topics in the Everquest Message Boards and you will see what I mean.  &quot;Abashi--nerfed again...read this&quot;.  I mean what the hell kind of subject line is that?  What the hell is that post supposed to be about?<br>
<br>
Arg...I could go on for hours.  Be creative, people...write clearly and intelligently or you just betray your own personal worth.<br>
